    <bodyTop>
      <Value><![CDATA[<p>Need some extra Christmas cheer? Enjoy wearing jumpers in this cold weather? Like supporting a good cause?</p>
<p>Then get into the spirit and dig out your best festive woolly, or tinsel up a plain jumper.  Get ready to <em>make the world better with a sweater</em> on Friday 18th December for the fourth annual Christmas Jumper Day.</p>
<p>By donning your best festive sweater on Friday 18th December, you'll be helping raise money for Macmillan Cancer Support, Make-A-Wish® UK and Save the Children. 100% of your donations will be shared equally amongst these three charities, going directly to support vital work both in the UK and abroad.</p>
<p>The team text code from last year will not be available this time, however, there are a number of different ways to donate:</p>
<p><strong>Text / SMS Message</strong> - Donate £5 by texting the word SANTA5 to 70760 or donate £10 by texting SANTA10 to 70760.</p>
<p><strong>Online</strong> – Donate by going to the Text Santa website (itv.com/textsanta) and following the links. JustGiving operates the online donation platform.</p>
<p><strong>Phone</strong> – Call 0300 123 6060 (standard geographical charges may apply) to donate using a credit or debit card.</p>
<p><strong>Barclays bank transaction</strong><strong> -  </strong> Visit any branch of Barclays and pay in your money to the following bank account:  ITV Text Santa Barclays PLC / Account: 33197654 / Sort code: 207898</p>
<p>Last date for donations for text &amp; phone is 5pm on the 8th January 2016.  Last date for donations for online is 5pm on the 29th February 2016.</p>
<p><strong>Merry Christmas everyone</strong>!</p>]]></Value>
